会上登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo-Lars-Ulrich@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>戴夫·隆巴多 (Dave Lombardo) 公开反对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>鼓手拉尔斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lars-ulrich">·乌尔里希 (Lars Ulrich)</a>经常受到的批评，声称他“警告”那些“说他坏话”的人。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/empire-state-bastard-interview-biffy-clyro-simon-neil-mark-vennart-dave-lombardo-debut-album-3448598">帝国大厦混蛋：“我们将不惜一切代价走向绝境”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位鼓手曾是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">Slayer</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/testament">Testament</a>的成员，现在在极端金属项目<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/empire-state-bastard">Empire State Bastard</a>中演奏，他在<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/news/dave-lombardo-defends-lars-ulrich" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Metal Hammer</em></a>的新采访中公开反对人们对这位鞭打音乐家的仇恨，并表达了他的观点。对乌尔里希的赞赏。</p><p>当采访者询问 Lombardo 是否认为这位 Metallica 鼓手被许多金属乐迷不公平地忽视，并且他对乐队的影响力经常被忽视时，对话就出现了。</p><p> “绝对地！”他说。 “我告诫那些说他坏话的人，我不喜欢这样。你必须接受 Lars 是谁，以及他对 Metallica 音乐的贡献。”</p><p>他还解释说，他在最近的一次采访中看到另一位传奇金属鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">——Gojira</a>的Mario Duplantier——急忙为Ulrich辩护，并完全同意他的立场。 </p><figure id="attachment_3357622" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3357622" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3357622" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270.jpg" alt="Metallica 的拉斯·乌尔里希" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/2022_larsulrich_metallica_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3357622" class="wp-caption-text"> Metallica 乐队的 Lars Ulrich 将于 2022 年 7 月 28 日在芝加哥格兰特公园的 Lollapalooza 表演（图片来源：Scott Legato/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> “我最近看到马里奥·杜普兰蒂尔（Mario Duplantier）谈论拉尔斯，说了一些客气的话，”他回忆道，他指的是今年早些时候在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MMCwhCU5OUg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Downbeat</em></a>播客上接受的最近一次采访。 “我觉得拉斯是乐队的重要组成部分——任何其他人，听起来都会不一样。”</p><p> “[Metallica] 他们是一支非常鼓舞人心的乐队，每个人都想像他们一样强大，而你只能通过冒险来做到这一点，”他继续说道。 “当他们剪头发或做其他事情时，人们感到震惊，但这是他们进化的一部分，他们清楚地知道自己在做什么。我喜欢他们仍然在那里，表现出色。”</p><p>在接受媒体采访时，Lombardo 还透露了他欣赏的当代鼓手，特别是 Exodus 的 Tom Hunting。</p><p> “有很多伟大的鼓手，我无法只指出一位，”他说。 “对我来说，《出埃及记》中的汤姆·亨廷是我第一个看到的。当我们离开洛杉矶前往旧金山时，我看到他们，心想‘这家伙太棒了，你知道吗？他依然是！ </p><figure id="attachment_3484510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484510" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Mr. Bungle 的 Dave Lombardo 将于 2023 年 5 月 23 日在福克斯剧院演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Dave-Lombardo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484510" class="wp-caption-text"> Mr. Bungle 的 Dave Lombardo 于 2023 年 5 月 23 日在福克斯剧院演出。图片来源：Tim Mosenfelder/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>我们在《遗嘱》中和那些家伙一起表演了一场演出，那个家伙比以往任何时候都更强大。在（去年与胃癌作斗争）之后，他惊人地卷土重来，我为他感到骄傲，我很高兴能像我一样多次见到这些人。”</p><p>目前，Lombardo 是新极端金属乐队 Empire State Bastard 的成员，该乐队由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biffy-clyro">Biffy Clyro</a>成员 Simon Neil 和 Mike Vennart 组建。</p><p>这支四人乐队由 Bitch Falcon 的贝斯手 Naomi Macleod 完成，将于下个月发行他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-state-bastard-announce-debut-album-rivers-of-heresy-3450085">《Rivers Of Heresy》</a> ，并将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-state-bastard-announce-uk-and-european-headline-tour-buy-tickets-3481273">今年晚些时候开始英国和欧洲巡演</a>。</p><p> Neil 在最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/empire-state-bastard-interview-biffy-clyro-simon-neil-mark-vennart-dave-lombardo-debut-album-3448598" target="_blank" rel="noopener">接受 NME 的<em>In Conversation</em>系列采访</a>时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/empire-state-bastard-on-snaring-dave-lombardo-and-taking-him-to-greggs-and-lidl-3457510">透露了他们如何设法让 Lombardo 加入</a>阵容。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Empire State Bastard 与 Dave Lombardo 畅谈他们的重金属超级组合" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iO5GYR91XJs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在讨论中，他透露，他和维纳特花了两周时间讨论可以“像戴夫·隆巴多一样演奏”的鼓手，然后在大流行期间的一天，他们说：“我们他妈的应该得到戴夫·隆巴多的地址并给他发电子邮件吗？”</p><p> “他真的理解我们想用这张专辑和乐队做什么，”他们告诉 NME。 “他很忙，有很多事情需要联系他，但当他回来后就说，‘这很特别，我要做，我要和你一起演奏并制作这张唱片’——就在那时我们说，‘好吧，这他妈的正在发生。’”</p><p>在与<em>NME</em>的讨论中，尼尔将 ESB 描述为“不惜一切代价走向极端”，并开始了“极其可怕的音乐之旅”。</p><p> “因为我们在 Biffy 一起玩，所以我们没有必要做另一个感觉相距很远的项目，”他解释道。 “这是我最讨厌的事情，当人们离开他们的全职乐队去做另一件事时，这只是与他们正在做的事情略有不同的版本。他妈的有什么意义？”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slayers-dave-lombardo-defends-metallica-lars-ulrich-admonish-people-who-talk-shit-3484508">《Slayer》的 Dave Lombardo 为 Metallica 的 Lars Ulrich 辩护：“我告诫那些说他坏话的人”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Linus Tech Tips 发生了什么以及为什么停止生产？ https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/whats-happening-with-linus-tech-tips-and-why-has-it-halted-product-3484436?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=whats-与莱纳斯技术提示一起发生的事情以及为什么它停止了生产Imogen DonovanThu, 17 Aug 2023 12:20:22 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3484436 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们将聘请一名外部调查员来调查这些指控”</p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/whats-happening-with-linus-tech-tips-and-why-has-it-halted-production-3484436">Linus Tech Tips 发生了什么以及为什么停止生产？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/linus-tech-tips-acknowledges-mistakes-and-address-accusations-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>围绕 Linus Tech Tips（一个评论流行科技产品的 YouTube 频道）的争议因其办公室“仓促”评论和厌女症的指控而成为头条新闻。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/safety-is-never-done-on-twitch-why-the-streaming-giant-is-gearing-up-to-protect-streamers-3306573">“Twitch 上的安全永远不会被忽视”：为什么这家流媒体巨头正准备保护流媒体</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/linus-tech-tips-temporarily-halts-operations-puts-out-apology-video-linus-made-a-clear-and-egregious-judgment-error/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PC Gamer</a></em>报道，创始人 Linus Sebastian 在 6 月 24 日发布的视频中<a href="https://youtu.be/P2hey3mNnN0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">错误地将 Billet Labs Monoblock 原型集成到 GeForce GTX 4090 GPU 上，</a>尽管该原型设计用于与 GTX 3090 配合使用。</p><p>该评论随后<a href="https://youtu.be/FGW3TPytTjc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">遭到竞争对手频道 Gamers Nexus 的批评</a>，他们表示 Linus Tech Tips 评论的“准确性、道德和责任”应该受到批评。该团队还声称，Monoblock 视频是为了“数量重于质量”而“匆忙推出内容”的一个例子。</p><p>尽管塞巴斯蒂安不再是 Linus Tech Tips 的首席执行官，但他对 Gamers Nexus <a href="https://linustechtips.com/topic/1526180-gamers-nexus-alleges-lmg-has-insufficient-ethics-and-integrity/page/16/#comment-16078641" target="_blank" rel="noopener">做出了回应</a>，因为在 Billet Labs Monoblock 审查时他仍然是该公司的带头人。</p><p> “我们正在经历一些成长的烦恼——为了透明度，我们一直非常公开地谈论它们——很明显，我们在内部流程和沟通方面还有一些工作要做，”他说，并补充说，他“没有表现出“Billet 处于最佳状态”，因为他“不想让任何人购买它（因为无论它在什么温度下运行，这都是一种严重的金钱浪费）”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我们现在干什么？" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0cTpTMl8kFY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这仍然没有缓和球迷的情绪，他们指责塞巴斯蒂安<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/LinusTechTips/comments/15rtfe2/why_didnt_linus_just_own_his_mistakes_apologize/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">没有“承认自己的错误”</a> 。因此，8 月 16 日，Linus Tech Tips 高层领导的几位成员上传了一段新的道歉视频，称“还有很多工作要做”。</p><p>首席执行官 Terren Tong 表示，Sebastian 因处理 Billet Labs Monoblock 事件的方式而受到警告，“在重新测试他认为不切实际的产品方面存在明显且严重的判断错误”。</p><p> “我欠你们更好的，我很抱歉，”创始人道歉。 “伙计们，我还将花一周时间重新关注最重要的事情，这将为你们带来我们能制作的最好的该死的内容。”</p><p>然而，粉丝们却贬低了 Linus Tech Tips 商店和赞助商的宣传以及视频整体不敬的基调。此外，前 Linus Tech Tips 社交媒体经理 Madison Reeve 指责 YouTube 频道营造了厌恶女性的工作环境。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">为了停止猜测和我收到的DM。<br />我选择辞去 LTT 的职务，因为它以及我面临的工作环境正在破坏我的心理健康。</p><p> The number of daily items the Social media role at the time was expected to fill was incredibly high.</p><p> — Madison | Suop (@suuuoppp) <a href="https://twitter.com/suuuoppp/status/1691693740254228741?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 16, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Through a series of posts to X (formerly Twitter), Reeve claimed that her mental health suffered while she was on the team, and that she “would not have recommended anyone I knew to work there, especially with my experiences as a woman in the office”.</p><p> Speaking to <em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/linus-tech-tips-temporarily-halts-operations-puts-out-apology-video-linus-made-a-clear-and-egregious-judgment-error/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PC Gamer</a></em> , Tong said that he was “in a state of shock” reading what Reeve had to share about her experiences. “They aren&#39;t consistent with our company values. They are not consistent with my experience with the team in the six weeks or so that I&#39;ve been here,” he replied.</p><p> “Our HR team will be conducting a more thorough assessment of the allegations. Furthermore, we will also be hiring an outside investigator to look into the allegations and will commit to publishing the findings and implementing any corrective actions that may arise because of this,” he continued.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/creative-assembly">Creative Assembly</a> &#39;s colourful shooter <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hyenas"><em>Hyenas</em></a> has announced <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sci-fi-shooter-hyenas-announces-chaotic-closed-beta-with-eight-unique-operators-3483829">a closed beta for PC players</a> at the end of this month.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/whats-happening-with-linus-tech-tips-and-why-has-it-halted-production-3484436">What&#39;s happening with Linus Tech Tips and why has it halted production?</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
